在[[彼得·傑克森|彼得·傑克森]]執導的《[[哈比人電影系列|哈比人電影系列]]》，朵力由[[馬克·哈德洛|馬克·哈德洛]]飾演<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0109143/|title=Dori (Character)|accessdate=2018-04-13|publisher=IMDB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108161645/http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0109143/|archivedate=2017年1月8日|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://middleearthnews.com/2011/07/20/nori-ori-and-dori-a-character-synopsis/|title=Nori, Ori, and Dori: A Character Synopsis|accessdate=2018-04-13|date=2011-07-20|publisher=Middle-earth News|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115222552/http://middleearthnews.com/2011/07/20/nori-ori-and-dori-a-character-synopsis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片裡將朵力、諾力和歐力描繪為同母異父的三兄弟，年紀最大的朵力時常要照看著諾力和歐力<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.empireonline.com/interviews/interview.asp?IID=1598|title=The Hobbit Interviews: Mark Hadlow On Dori|work=Empire Online|accessdate=2018-09-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126051727/http://www.empireonline.com/interviews/interview.asp?IID=1598|archivedate=2013-01-26}}</ref>。

